channel.title: Help: No response from server. Please try a using different world
channel.description:
When I get on Mopar and type in all my info, it says this on Mopar: No response from server. Please try using a different world. And this on the runserver: Potential null 76.97.31.58 is checking server status.
Any help with this? I am using PvpScape source. I JUST added the drill seargent tut, along with the pSay method. Id love if anyone could help, especially Lothy, since he/she made PvpScape.

item.title: Help: No response from server. Please try a using different world
item.dc:creator: @Bradness Bradness
item.description:
@Bradness wrote:

Fix: First, go into characters folder and click all of the admin accounts, and change the energy to 100. Then, go into server.java and change the port to 5555. Compile, run, try to log in under port 5555 (File > New Port). Next, Close server, change port back to 43594, compile, run, file>new port 43594. Log in, and it should work.

EDIT: Great… Now its acting up again…
